name: VOID (itch) (Witherskeleton)
description:
Adventure through a strange world with a cat, a slime, and a scientist. Features 3-4 hours of content with loads of optional junk. Features:

- Enjoyable RPG combat!
- Unique battle sprites!
- An orchestral classical soundtrack!
- Humorous writing and characters!

So feel free to download it if you want.
